      • stop

        public void stop()
        Stops the internal threads of the ARStreamReader2Resender.

      • dispose

        public boolean dispose()
        Deletes the ARStreamReader2Resender.
        This function should only be called after stop()

        Warning: If this function returns false, then the ARStreamReader2Resender was not disposed !
        Returns:
        true if the Runnables are not running.
        false if the ARStreamReader2Resender could not be disposed now.
